releaseNotes:
Release 5.44.7.1
* RVM 2 Integration, feel free to explore the RVM release notes:
     This release integrates the ,
     Breaking change:
     This feature introduces a breaking change, the local assets previously organized as:
          Assets
                Runtime
                     5.44.7.35 (should be the extension less file from http://developer.openfin.co/release/runtime/5.44.7.35)
               RVM
                     latestVersion ( a text file without any extension that just contains the string 0.1.0.43)
                     OpenfinRVM.exe (the executable with the version 0.1.0.43)
     The new structure should be:
          Assets
                Runtime
                     5.44.7.35 (should be the extension less file from http://developer.openfin.co/release/runtime/5.44.7.35)
               RVM
                     latestVersion ( a text file without any extension that just contains the string RVM version: e.g. 2.0.0.1)
                     latest (should be the extension less file from http://developer.openfin.co/release/rvm/2.0.0.1)

* Added large message support for InterApplicationBus Publish.
* Added support for JArrays for InterApplicationBus Publish.
* Removed the need for write access on the execution folder the RuntimeOptions.ConfigBasePath option is now deprecated.
* Added Event for when the core process is terminated

* Fixed issue where windows initiated from window.Open or a hyperlink were not connecting to the runtime
* Fixed issue where native rendered HTML5 controls (dropdown, date picker) were not closed upon parent window move.
* Fixed issue where Embedded Views would sporadically fail to load after install in Windows XP.
* Fixed issue where Embedded Views with IFrames would not connect under 5.44.X

You can explore these changes on the 5.44.7.1 Docs
